events.name: 30 Minutes Towards Better Bibliographies and Footnotes! (online)
events.details: This 30-minute workshop will focus on Zotero, but will also briefly introduce you to other similar tools, including Mendeley and Endnote. We will cover setting up an account, importing citations from library databases and web pages, and deploying the references into a Word document. Please watch this six-minute video before the workshop: https://vimeo.com/369873151

about: Princeton University is a private institution that was founded in 1746. It has a total undergraduate enrollment of 5,321 (fall 2021), its setting is suburban, and the campus size is 600 acres. It utilizes a semester-based academic calendar. Princeton University's ranking in the 2022-2023 edition of Best Colleges is National Universities, #1. Its tuition and fees are $57,410.
